olith with their choice of:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A spreadsheet and text files (for extremely simple sites)."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Specialized systems tailored to their use case, such as Shopify + Salsify + Bazaarvoice for an e-commerce site."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A headless cloud CMS with rich content modelling capabilities, such as Contentful."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"second-pick-a-ui-development-library"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#second-pick-a-ui-development-library","ariaLabel":"second pick a ui development library permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Second, pick a UI development library"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/blog/2018-10-11-rise-of-modern-web-development"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"React and Angular are both excellent, ubiquitious, modern choices"}]},{"type":"text","value":", with rich community ecosystems to address website-specific concerns like:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SEO"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Routing"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accessibility"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"i18n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"third-choose-a-performance-strategy"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#third-choose-a-performance-strategy","ariaLabel":"third choose a performance strategy permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Third, choose a performance strategy"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"There are two main approaches to performance — "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/blog/2018-10-16-why-mobile-performance-is-crucial#how-performance-optimization-works"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"payload optimization and delivery optimization"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Payload optimization involves performance-enhancing development practices. Delivery optimization means compiling websites to static files that can be served from a global CDN, rather than running servers and databases."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Often, to ensure a fast site, you’ll need both."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To do delivery optimization, you’ll need to pick a JAMStack site generator like Hugo or Gatsby."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To do payload optimization, your team will need to implement a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2019/01/front-end-performance-checklist-2019-pdf-pages/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"long performance checklist"}]},{"type":"text","value":", or pick a framework such as Gatsby that "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/features/#legend"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"performs payload optimization"}]},{"type":"text","value":" out of the box."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"fourth-choose-your-content-mesh"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#fourth-choose-your-content-mesh","ariaLabel":"fourth choose your content mesh permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","ve