"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"automatically makes your site fast out of the box"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"figure","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-link"],"href":"/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/f4c82/content-mesh.png","style":"display: block","target":"_blank","rel":["noopener"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"],"style":"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 786px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-background-image"],"style":"padding-bottom: 61.18925831202047%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-image"],"style":"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px #ffffff;","alt":"The modern website landscape","title":"","src":"/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/75efb/content-mesh.png","srcSet":["/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/bea6c/content-mesh.png 197w","/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/9f6c6/content-mesh.png 393w","/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/75efb/content-mesh.png 786w","/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/43bd5/content-mesh.png 1179w","/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/f4c82/content-mesh.png 1564w"],"sizes":["(max-width:","786px)","100vw,","786px"]},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"figcaption","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n   The Content Mesh integrates "},{"type":"element","tagName":"b","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"headless"}]},{"type":"text","value":" content systems, modern development tools, and website performance\n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"content-mesh-alternatives"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#content-mesh-alternatives","ariaLabel":"content mesh alternatives permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Content Mesh Alternatives"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Website teams searching for a content mesh can consider:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"utilizing vendor integrations"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"assorted JAMStack solutions"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While some solutions have "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"part"}]},{"type":"text","value":" of the puzzle, only Gatsby comes with out-of-the-box CMS integrations, a modern development framework, and cutting-edge performance."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Content vendor integrations"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"One option for website teams is to use existing vendor integrations to glue CMS systems together."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For example, a team could build a site with Shopify, using their Liquid Template engine, pull in product listing data from Salsify, and reviews from Bazaarvoice."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While this can solve the CMS integration problem, it locks the website in an idiosyncratic development environment without helping solve website performance."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Assorted JAMStack solutions"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Another option is the JAMstack space, with a proliferation of tools that make sites fast. These tools tend to "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"either"}]},{"type":"text","value":" support modern development frameworks "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"or"}]},{"type":"text","value":" connect to content systems, but not both."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For example, VuePress and Nuxt.js allow teams to build sites in Vue, but don’t offer connections with any enterprise content systems — they require content to be stored as markdown files within the code repository."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Middleman allows connections to third-party data sources, though currently only DatoCMS and Contentful are supported."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby is the only content mesh option that creates fast websites, supports modern development frameworks, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"and"}]},{"type":"text","value":" connects to enterprise content systems. Gatsby features:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Integrations with 120+ backends"}]},{"type":"text","value":", including 15+ enterprise content systems like Wordpress, Drupal, Contentful, Contentstack, Salsify and Shopify, as well as the ability to add additional sources."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A React development environment"}]},{"type":"text","value":", along with key plugins that provide key website features like SEO, routing, accessibility, and i18n."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lightning-fast out-of-the-box performance"}]},{"type":"text","value":", including both payload and delivery optimizations."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"conclusion"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#conclusion","ariaLabel":"conclusion permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Conclusion"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Yesterday, publishing on the web was difficult. The CMS emerged as a single application to store content and build sites."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Today, the CMS is being reimagined."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"With maturity comes growing functionality and complexity; a shift from monolithic to modular architectures."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Today, there’s a multitude of vendors, frameworks, and approaches for content modelling, authentication, search, analytics, payments, development environemnt, performance, and so on."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The key question becomes: how to bring these pieces into a unified whole?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Yesterday, our challenge was "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"creating a digital experience"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Today, our challenge is "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"making that experience incredible"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"excerpt":"This is Part 5, the conclusion of a series. Part 1 is   The Journey to a Content Mesh ; Part 2 is   Unbundling of the CMS ; Part 3 is   The…","timeToRead":5,"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2018-10-18-creating-compelling-content-experiences/","publishedAt":null},"frontmatter":{"title":"Journey to the Content Mesh Conclusion: Creating Compelling Content Experiences","excerpt":null,"date":"October 18th 2018","ra